quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  23,18,"Ne khweshia amatsi kayelele okhurula mwikulu mana nikhukawotselesia khwiloba, ne toto efwe khuli nende obunyali bwokhukayiniaho."
  23,19,"Khu amatsi ako nikhubamesilia emikunda chietsitende nende tsizabibu, munyoolangamwo ebiamo ebinji biamulitsanga."
  23,20,"Nende omusala kurulanga khushikulu shia Sinai, kurusinjia amafura okhuba kokhutongwamwo khubalia."
  23,21,"Ne toto mutsisolo mulimwo nende ameeko, khubanywesinjia khubilia bili mutsinda tsiatsio, ne munyoolangamwo obukhoonyi obunji, ne etsindimwo mutsiliitsanga."
  23,22,"Ne hekulu watsio nende khubwaro muchingungwa."
  23,23,"Ne toto khwaruma Nuhu khubandu bebe, mana naboola mbu; “Enywe Abandu banje, laame Nyasaye. Mubula nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe, kho shimuritsangakhwo tawe?""
  23,24,"Mana omukanda kwabakhongo babakhayi mubandu bebe nikuboola mbu; “Uno shini shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu shinga enywe, yenyanga okhwikhola omulayi khwinywe, ne Nyasaye yenyanga (okhubechesia), yakheshiye Abamalaika. Efwe shikhwawulilakhwo kano khubakofu befu bakhale tawe."
  23,25,"Uno shali shiosishiosi tawe halali ni Omundu uli nende lilalu. Mumulindilile butswa hatiti.""
  23,26,"(Nuhu) naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esye, toto bano bamalile okhukhaya.”"
  23,27,"Mana nikhumufimbulila mbu; “Kasia eliaro imbeli wetsimoni tsiefu nende obufimbuli bwefu. Kho olwa likhuwa liefu liliula, mana lichiko libitikhe amatsi, awo injisiamwo okhurula mubuli tsimbia bibili bibili, nende Abandu bobo, halali ulia owelikhuwa lilie liamala okhubura (mbu oyo yakhasishe). Kho olaboola ninasi khubalia abakholela obubii emioyo chiabu tawe. Toto abo balasishibwa.”"